    <string name="info_how">
    "How to use the application:\n\n"
"1. Click the '+' button to add new medications.\n"
"2. Fill in the name, form of the medication, dosage and select the course of administration and number of doses per day. \n"
"3. To receive reminders, add the times of administration by clicking on the 'Add reminder time' button.\n"
"4. Add the information 'How to take' and 'Notes'\n"
"5. If you click 'Other' in the 'Form of medication' and 'How to take' fields, you can enter personal data that is not in the list\n"
"6. Save the medication and go to the main screen.\n"
"7. On the main screen, you can see the cards of all your medications and track the medication intake.\n"
"8. To edit the medication, swipe the medication card to the right. After editing, click the 'Save changes' button.\n"
"9. To delete the medication, swipe the medication card to the right. Click the 'Delete' button.\n This will also delete all reception history.\n"
"10. To view your medication history, swipe the medication card to the left. To return to the main screen, click the arrow.\n"
    "11. To configure the application, click the gear icon."</string>
